values:
Popcorn.&nbsp; Bad.

I just DDRed 400 calories to get rid of it.&nbsp; This is day 4.&nbsp; There have been some "fasting mess ups" but they have been fixed by over exercise or walking.&nbsp;&nbsp;

I hope to walk a lot, today, with my friend, and yeah.&nbsp; 

I might get a salad.&nbsp; &gt;.&lt;&nbsp; Due to social influences.&nbsp; But that's OK, I will live.

Oh, and I need help.&nbsp; How do you convince your boyfriend that you're not hungry when HE'S ALWAYS HUNGRY AND ALWAYS WANTS TO EAT.&nbsp; AH!&nbsp; This is going to be difficult.&nbsp; What to do . . . Hm.

Ugh, I need to walk a lot, today.&nbsp; REALLY BADLY.

My friend should be ready by like 5.&nbsp; Hm.&nbsp; Ok.&nbsp; And I'll try to exercise before that, too.&nbsp;&nbsp;

Monday, I am done, and I can eat "SOMETHING."&nbsp; As in, something normal.&nbsp; Woo.

I'm not really hungry, anyway.

I'll explain.

I woke up early to watch my brother, and then went back to bed, UNTIL 1:15.&nbsp; Which was a mistake.&nbsp; I hate sleeping late, I feel lazy.&nbsp; I don't stay up until 5AM, jeez.

But I didn't eat anything all day, and went to a concert.&nbsp; But the day was pretty wasted.&nbsp;

Eh.

Today, I have a party, hopefully, I'll resist.&nbsp; Maybe just A LITTLE.&nbsp; If there are vegetables, great.&nbsp; But I doubt it.&nbsp; This isn't catered.&nbsp; Lol.

I'm playing a bit of DDR (what I can stand) and walking to the party (an hour and a half), so yeah, it should be cool.

So I can make it through a week without eating, I MAY start drinking caffeine/taking pills.&nbsp; I have diet pills, and I'll take them before the party, just in case.&nbsp; On wednesday, friday and sunday, I'm taking my friend's stolen ADD medication (lol), cause it makes me hyper.&nbsp; Woo.&nbsp;&nbsp;

And tonight I may drink caffiene at the party.&nbsp; MAY.&nbsp;&nbsp;

And you know how there are salads with shit loads of calories, and than there are salads with none.&nbsp; Salads with NONE are good for going out places (such as my 3 friends' "goodbye" party for college).&nbsp;&nbsp;

I've got this all worked out.&nbsp; Ah.&nbsp; I'm so happy.&nbsp; No eating until&nbsp;sunday.&nbsp; Hoo.&nbsp; Lots of water.&nbsp; And then, I'll slowly incorporate food back, with vegetables, fruits, et cetera.&nbsp;&nbsp;

I'm only happy when I'm starving, yes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

Until tomorrow, adieu.

Ok, so my "last two days of starving before camp" died.&nbsp; Friday was good, but yesterday was pretty bad.&nbsp; Not BAD but pretty bad (As in I ate like a normal person and I am hopefully maintaining my weight).&nbsp; 

I guess that's good, though, so I'm not all fucked up for camp.

EEK, it's making me all fucked up.&nbsp; So, I need to NOT fuck up.&nbsp; :P

I'm a camel eater, so I probably won't eat much, today, and go from there.&nbsp; 

'Cause today they are only serving dinner.&nbsp; At 4:30 (SO EARLY =D)

I'm going to be so thin when I get out of here (LOOK AT HOW SURE I AM OF THIS).

SO, 7 days of starvation.&nbsp; I get back at 3 on sunday, so yeah, I can't eat!&nbsp; :X&nbsp; I think I'll hang out with the boyfriend.&nbsp; Or the girlfriend (lol).&nbsp; 

I MUST STAY STRONG (I'm really worried about fucking up.)

&lt;3

But I'm staying in the attic with the computer.

Ugh, I'm worried.&nbsp; I need to go be active, 'cause I had ice cream and an omelette (SP?), today.

But at the beach, it isn't hard.&nbsp; Running around, boardwalk, et cetera.&nbsp; I'm not worried.&nbsp; 

Yeah, this vacation hasn't been bad.&nbsp; At all.&nbsp; 

Tomorrow, just TCBY, then hardxcore not eating, cause I love it.&nbsp; I love the feeling of blacking out (happened on thursday, friday, saturday, parts of sunday), cause you haven't eaten.&nbsp; Ah.

I want to wyle.

I'm going to put this here: GW: 110.

There.&nbsp; Too bad I don't know how much I weigh.&nbsp; 

BAH.

I get random bursts of energy.&nbsp; Must do something.&nbsp; Bye.

'Ey, I'm at the beach, and I didn't eat anything on thursday, friday = two salads, yesterday = some pizza, today = nothing yet, but not a lot, because of yesterday.&nbsp;&nbsp;

I'm having little black out moments.&nbsp; It's good.&nbsp;

And today I'm going to the beach, so that means active shit.&nbsp; More calories burned!&nbsp;

I already went on a bike ride this morning.&nbsp;&nbsp;

Coming back, tomorrow.

I have to burn 300 calories of DDR.

Walk around with Steff.

Either walk around by myself or play DDR until Fuddruckers.

I'm not really hungry (lol) so I'll just get a diet coke.&nbsp; 

&gt;.&lt;

D'ah!

Do you ever get that feeling that your heart is beating really hard and you can feel it (which is bad)?

I didn't really eat much, yesterday, walked for 4-5 hours, was very active otherwise, played DDR, et cetera, and I woke up this morning with my lack of caffeine high and this WEAK feeling.&nbsp; 

My rich friend wants to take me to a steak house, so I'm going, and getting a salad.&nbsp; I WILL BEAT TEMPATION OF THIER STUPID TORTILLAS AND FRIED SHIT!

I have work for six and a half hours, today, too, which helps, and I do the laborous job of pushing carts.&nbsp; The whole time.&nbsp; It's a lot of work, trust me.&nbsp; And I guess I'll save some salad for work, too, since I probably won't be able to eat it all since I'll be diet coking it up (I love free refills).

I wish I wasn't scared of the scale.&nbsp; X.X&nbsp; If my "fast" works this week, I'll weigh myself monday.&nbsp; AH!

Why is FAST in quotes, you ask?

I have this HYPERWORKOUTAHOLIC thing that I do -- For instance, if I eat, say, 300 calories of something, I walk for 2-3 hours to burn it off, or play 600 calories of DDR.&nbsp; It's gone, regardless, those calories won't touch me this week.&nbsp; I will be in the negatives.&nbsp; 

So, basically, I eat, (usually very little), and MUST GO IN THE NEGATIVES.

And I have to do this until monday.&nbsp; 

What do you guys think?

So, I drank caffeine, but I probably won't drink any, today.&nbsp; 

I went hiking, DDR'd and what not.

Don't you hate it when you do all this exercise and then you eat a lot, and your stomach feels fat?&nbsp; But you know you burned it off in technical calories.

I'm DDRing all morning, and then wylin' at a rave!&nbsp; 

UGH, I hate the after effects of laxatives -- it takes a while to take your next poopy 'without help.'&nbsp; HA, to be honest.

And my stomach is killing me because it's full and stuff is probably just SITTING there.&nbsp; 

I'm pretty excited about getting professional help (hopefully) 'cause the government (yikes) knows about my ED, now.&nbsp; Thank you, neglectful parents!&nbsp; If I tell them that I eat barely anything a day and I'm still "fat" they should help me find a place where I can get my metabolism checked.&nbsp; This'll be great.&nbsp; 

Don't you hate it how you feel like you ruined the "week" and you want to start "next week" fasting and shit?&nbsp; Ugh, it's weird.&nbsp; 

All that I know is that this weekend is going to be wylin'.&nbsp; :D 

I barely worked at all this week.&nbsp; It kind of sucked, I like structure.

OK, SUMMERSTAR63, you know who you are.&nbsp; Starting MONDAY-FRIDAY, we shouldn't eat.&nbsp; Anything.&nbsp; We keep saying this, lol, but seriously.&nbsp; This time.&nbsp; :P

It sucks, 'cause, yeah, you have to eat around your boyfriends.&nbsp;&nbsp; 

But I didn't eat much, so yay!&nbsp; 

Yesterday was weird.&nbsp; I stopped drinking caffeine and I feel like I'm dizzy and confused and "not here."&nbsp; My caffeine state-of-mind had become ME.&nbsp; 

Eh.
